Partner now surprises you with a jump to 3\S!.  

Wow! Partner has 16 and you have more than that. Slam appears certain, by why not check for Aces? So you bid 4NT and partner answers 5\C. What do you say next? 

You probably say "Oh Darn!" or perhaps something less printable. But then you just sign of at 5\S.}

